CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Immunome Inc is a biopharmaceutical company. It is engaged in utilizing proprietary human memory B cell platform to discover and develop first-in-class antibody therapeutics designed to change the way diseases are currently being treated. The company's primary focus areas are oncology and infectious disease, including COVID-19.
